name: "Sigh" Cake - Ozone flavor
description: @Sugartivi | Dear art collector, sometimes the best way to deal when things are not going our way - is to really feel the disappointment. This is hard but it lets us move onward. This Sigh cake is ozone flavored: Ozone is the sweet, zingy smell and taste that you find in the air before a thunderstorm. It’s created when lightning splits nitrogen and oxygen molecules in the atmosphere.
